       <xref ref-type="bibr">
        34
       </xref>
       ), was incubated with 10 μ
       <span>
        m
       </span>
       of SufBC
       <sub>
        2
       </sub>
       D-FADH
       <sub>
        2
       </sub>
       (0.93 FADH
       <sub>
        2
       </sub>
       /complex). Ferrozine was added, and formation of the ferrozine-Fe
       <sup>
        2+
       </sup>
       complex was followed at 562 nm.
      </p>
     </sec>
