         </em>
         = 10, 15, 20, and 30 min (
         <em>
          dashed bold black line
         </em>
         )) showing formation of the neutral semiquinone species (FADH
         <sup>
          ·
         </sup>
         ) at 590 nm (maximum formation at 7 min (
         <em>
          black line
         </em>
         )).
         <em>
